	%<- ({d ofkd X A} {dm mofkd d met/unit} {y} {e' isvar y J} cut-ofkd M1 ([e] D1 d y e) ([e] [em] D3 d dm y e em) (cxt-lookup/hit (DB y e')) (D1' d y e') (D3' d dm y e'))
